            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01RwkLQmxdqnUvUSV7riBPHK\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! Let me create a summary of what was found and fixed:\\n\\n## FIXED\\n\\nI've successfully added L10.createLead() instrumentation to the landing page. Here's what I found and fixed:\\n\\n### Components Reviewed:\\n1. **Hero.tsx** - ✅ FIXED - Added L10.createLead() instrumentation\\n2. **CTA.tsx** - ✅ FIXED - Added L10.createLead() instrumentation  \\n3. **Pricing.tsx** - ✅ No email capture (buttons only, no forms)\\n4. **Footer.tsx** - ✅ No email capture (navigation links only)\\n\\n### Changes Made:\\n\\n**Hero Component (`/src/components/Hero.tsx`):**\\n- ✅ Added `import { L10 } from '@/lib/tracking'`\\n- ✅ Added form state management (status, error)\\n- ✅ Added `handleSubmit` function that calls `L10.createLead(email)`\\n- ✅ Converted email input to a proper form with submit handler\\n- ✅ Added loading states, success message, and error handling\\n- ✅ Form shows success state after lead is captured\\n\\n**CTA Component (`/src/components/CTA.tsx`):**\\n- ✅ Added `import { L10 } from '@/lib/tracking'`\\n- ✅ Added form state management (status, error)\\n- ✅ Added `handleSubmit` function that calls `L10.createLead(email)`\\n- ✅ Converted email input to a proper form with submit handler\\n- ✅ Added loading states, success message, and error handling\\n- ✅ Form shows success state after lead is captured\\n\\nBoth components now properly:\\n- Validate email addresses before submission\\n- Call `L10.createLead(email)` on form submit\\n- Handle loading, success, and error states\\n- Display appropriate user feedback\\n- Clear the email field on success\\n\\nThe landing page is now fully instrumented for lead capture and conversion tracking! 🎉\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":128,\"cache_read_in