            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01QdnkF72JmMnUhwnUPnuAea\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"hasForm\\\": true,\\n  \\\"hasL10Import\\\": false,\\n  \\\"hasL10CreateLead\\\": false,\\n  \\\"needsInstrumentation\\\": true,\\n  \\\"summary\\\": \\\"CTA component has an email input field and 'Get Started Free' button, but lacks L10 import, form submission handler, and L10.createLead() call. The button currently does nothing on click.\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Details:**\\n- ✅ Has email capture form (Input + Button)\\n- ❌ Missing `import { L10 } from '@/lib/tracking'`\\n- ❌ Missing form submission handler\\n- ❌ Missing `L10.createLead(email)` call\\n- ❌ Missing success/error state handling\\n\\nThe component needs to be instrumented with proper form handling and L10 lead tracking.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":9993,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":9993,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":205,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
